2. Kaggle
✅ Offers free Python tutorials.
📊 Excellent hands-on practice with .csv, .xlsx, .json, etc. using pandas.
💡 You can upload your own files and write code in their online Jupyter environment.
💯 Completely free.



4. Hackerrank – Python
🎯 Practice file handling problems (especially .txt files).
🔄 Real input/output simulation.  
